**Summary of what was implemented:**

- **New file `src/commands/templates.ts`** — `hive templates` command with 4 subcommands:
  - `hive templates list` — shows all 7 bundled templates with name, description, and installation status (not installed / installed / modified)
  - `hive templates show <name>` — prints bundled template content to stdout
  - `hive templates install <name...>` — copies templates to `.claude/agents/`; skips existing unless `--force`
  - `hive templates diff <name>` — shows colorized unified diff between installed and bundled versions
- **`--dir <path>`** flag overrides the output directory (default: `.claude/agents/` relative to hive root)
- "Modified" detection via MD5 hash comparison of installed vs bundled content
- **`src/index.ts`** updated to import and register the new command
- All quality checks pass: typecheck, 113 tests (5 suites), build
